Cls
Echo "Converting themes from RTG to AGA..."
AGS:
If $PiStorm EQ "1"
 List >T:ThemeChange themes PAT #?.conf LFORMAT "searchreplace FROM %N TO %N SEARCH $501E1000 REPLACE $00029004 INPLACE"
ELSE
 List >T:ThemeChange themes PAT #?.conf LFORMAT "searchreplace FROM %N TO %N SEARCH $500A1000 REPLACE $00029004 INPLACE"
Endif
CD AGS:Themes
Ex T:ThemeChange
Echo ""
Echo "Setting default theme."
If $Pistorm EQ "1"
 Searchreplace FROM ags:ags2.conf TO ags:ags2.conf SEARCH $501E1000 REPLACE $00029004 INPLACE
Else
 Searchreplace FROM ags:ags2.conf TO ags:ags2.conf SEARCH $500A1000 REPLACE $00029004 INPLACE
Endif
CD AGS:Themes.ags
Rename "- Use RTG Screen -.rub" TO "- Use RTG Screen -.run"
Rename "- Use AGA Screen -.run" TO "- Use AGA Screen -.rub"
Echo ""
Echo "Process complete!"
Delete >NIL: T:ThemeChange
AGS: